--> Useful in database to improve the speed of data retrieval.
--> It is a data structure of table of contents that points us to the location where actual data lives. When
    we create an index on a column of the table, we store that column & a pointer to the whole row of the index.

-- Indexing type :-
a) ordered Indexing --> Column is sorted as per ascending order.
b) Hash Indexing --> Indexing is as pre hash function & Hash table 
